author: Lori Dorn
title: An Overly Excited Little Dog Stops to Check Out Something In the Corner During an Agility Course
text:
After a bit of a rough start , an excited little Jack Russell terrier named Olly was full of adrenaline as he soared high above the obstacles in the Crufts 2017 Dog Show agility course. Unfortunately, the excitement of the crowd caused Olly to occasionally miss his marks , particularly when he unexpectedly veered off course to sniff at something in the corner before continuing on.
